OL,3,C'It shouldn't happen': Disabled people
OL,4,Ccriticise poor access in town
OL,6,FHe says: "The main issue for me is if
OL,7,Fthere are cars parked, road signs or
OL,8,Funexpected roadworks."
OL,10,FMr De La Mare adds: "Everyday you'll
OL,11,Fget the traffic news on the radio and
OL,12,Fit will obviously explain all the
OL,13,Froads that are closed but it wouldn't
OL,14,Fusually say if certain pavements were
OL,15,Fclosed and that's an issue for me."
OL,17,FHe says he hopes to raise more
OL,18,Fawareness about pavements and
OL,19,Fpotential trip hazards for people with
OL,20,Faccessibility needs.
