OL,3,C'It shouldn't happen': Disabled people
OL,4,Ccriticise poor access in town
OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey says it is
OL,7,Factively trying to improve
OL,8,Finfrastructure where it can with a new
OL,9,Fzebra crossing recently installed
OL,10,Fbehind Elizabeth College.
OL,12,FRoad Safety Officer Paul James adds:
OL,13,F"We try and upgrade all of our
OL,14,Fcrossings whenever there is an
OL,15,Fopportunity, it could be during
OL,16,Fscheduled resurfacing projects or in
OL,17,Fthis case, we took the opportunity
OL,18,Fthat there was already a road closure
OL,19,Fhappening in the area."
